var e=JSON.parse(`[{"id":"L2_1","type":"subtitle","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"레드시프트 습격 <color=#ffd34c>이틀 뒤</color>","JPN":"レッドシフトの襲撃から<color=#ffd34c>二日後</color>","ENG":"<color=#ffd34c>Two days after</color> the Red Shift ambush","TWN":"紅移突襲 <color=#ffd34c>兩天后</color>","SCN":"红移突袭 <color=#ffd34c>两天后</color>","DEU":"<color=#ffd34c>Two days after</color> the Red Shift ambush","FRA":"<color=#ffd34c>Two days after</color> the Red Shift ambush"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L3_1","type":"subtitle","speaker":null,"text":{"KOREA":"<color=#ffd34c>조디악 나이츠 본부</color>\\n기사단 회의실 나이츠 홀","JPN":"<color=#ffd34c>ゾディアックナイツ本部</color>\\n騎士団会議室、ナイツホール","ENG":"[[","TWN":"<color=#ffd34c>十二宮騎士團總部</color>\\n騎士團會議室 騎士大廳","SCN":"<color=#ffd34c>十二宫骑士团总部</color>\\n骑士团会议室。骑士大厅。","DEU":"[[","FRA":"[["},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","slots":{"L":null,"C":null,"R":null}}},{"id":"L6_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","text":{"KOREA":"말도 안 돼…! 레드시프트 놈들이 무구를 복구해냈다고?","JPN":"そんな馬鹿な……！　レッドシフトのやつらが武具を復元しただと？","ENG":"Impossible...! Are you saying the Red Shift managed to restore the Armament?!","TWN":"這不可能…！紅移那些傢伙居然修復了武具？"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L7_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","text":{"KOREA":"별의 무구에 담긴 인도자의 정수를 그들이 깨우쳤다는 건가?","JPN":"星の武具に込められている導き手の真髄、それを彼らが呼び覚ましたということか？","ENG":"Does that mean they've unlocked the essence of the Star Guide embedded in the Armament?","TWN":"他們領悟了星之武具中蘊含的引導者精髓嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L8_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아뇨. 놈들의 무구는 겉모습을 흉내 낸 단순 레플리카에 불과했습니다.","JPN":"いいえ。やつらの武具は外見だけをコピーした、ただのレプリカでしたわ。","ENG":"No. Their so-called Armament was just a cheap replica mimicking the real thing.","TWN":"不，那些傢伙的武具只是模仿外觀的簡單複製品而已。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L9_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그들도 그것을 알기에 구원기사단의 고유무장을 사용하려는 것이죠.","JPN":"彼らもそれをわかっているから、救世騎士団の固有武装を利用しようとしているのです。","ENG":"They know it too, which is why they're after the Unique Gear of the Knights of Redemption.","TWN":"他們也知道這一點，所以才想使用救贖騎士團的專屬裝備。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L11_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_B","text":{"KOREA":"최악이군. 자칫하면 기사단이 숭앙하는 인도자에 대한 믿음이 뿌리째 뽑힐 거야.","JPN":"最悪だ。下手をすれば騎士団が持っている導き手への信頼が根こそぎ崩れてしまうだろう。","ENG":"This is the worst-case scenario. If this goes poorly, people might lose faith in the Guide we revere.","TWN":"真糟糕。如果不小心的話，騎士團對他們崇敬的引導者的信任可能會被徹底摧毀。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L12_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_B","text":{"KOREA":"각국에서 터진 문제를 대처하는 것만으로도 충분히 골치 아프거늘…….","JPN":"各国で発生した問題に対処するだけでも十分困っているというのに……","ENG":"We're already overwhelmed just handling the incidents erupting across the world...","TWN":"光是應對各國爆發的問題就已經夠頭痛的了……"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L13_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"말씀대로 현재 전세계적인 이상현상이 일어나고 있는 상황입니다.","JPN":"おっしゃるとおり、現在は全世界的に異常現象が発生している状況です。","ENG":"You're right. Strange phenomena are breaking out globally.","TWN":"正如你所說，目前全球範圍內正在發生異常現象。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L14_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"관리국의 지원은 기대할 수 없으니, 당장은 저희의 힘으로 그들을 막아야 해요.","JPN":"管理局の支援は期待できませんので、今は私たちの力で彼らを止めなければなりません。","ENG":"With no help coming from the Administration, we'll have to stop them on our own for now.","TWN":"無法指望管理局的支援，所以暫時我們得靠自己的力量阻止他們。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L17_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_B","text":{"KOREA":"헛소리. 현 상황에서 무구를 갖춘 이는 자네를 제외하곤 고작 셋이 아닌가?","JPN":"戯言を。今の状況で武具を持っている者は君以外に3人しかいないではないか。","ENG":"Nonsense. Outside of you, only three others have access to an Armament, don't they?","TWN":"胡說八道。現狀下，除了你之外，裝備武具的只有三個人，不是嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L18_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_B","text":{"KOREA":"그마저도 피오네 경을 제외하면 전력 미달이야! 멀쩡한 기사들을 사지로 내몰 수는 없네!!","JPN":"それもフィオネ卿を除くと、力不足だ！　まともな騎士たちを死なせるわけにはいかないのだ！！","ENG":"And without Dame Fione, that number barely counts as a force! We can't throw perfectly capable knights into a slaughter!","TWN":"即使是這樣，除了菲奧尼卿之外，戰力也不足！不能把正常的騎士們推向絕境！！"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_SERIOUS"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L19_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","text":{"KOREA":"침착하게. 카란티시르가 다른 단원들을 움직이지 않은 데에는 분명 이유가 있어.","JPN":"落ち着きたまえ。カランティシルが他の団員を動かしていないのには、きっと理由があるはずだ。","ENG":"Calm down. There's a reason Carantisir hasn't mobilized the other Red Shift knights yet.","TWN":"冷靜點。卡蘭堤西爾沒有調動其他成員，肯定有原因。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L20_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","text":{"KOREA":"레드시프트의 전력이 단둘이라면, 승산이 마냥 없지만은 않겠지.","JPN":"レッドシフトの戦力が二人だけなら、勝算がないわけではない。","ENG":"If it's just the two of them, we might still have a chance.","TWN":"如果紅移的戰力只有兩人，那勝算也不是完全沒有吧。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L22_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","text":{"KOREA":"각 가문에 병력을 차출할 수 있도록 전파하게.","JPN":"各家門に兵力を選び出すよう伝えるのだ。","ENG":"Send word to the houses to mobilize their troops.","TWN":"傳達給各家族，以便徵召兵力。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L23_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","text":{"KOREA":"그들이 노리기 전, 우리가 선수를 친다.","JPN":"彼らが狙ってくる前に、私たちが先手を打つ。","ENG":"We strike before they make their move.","TWN":"在他們動手之前，我們先發制人。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ELDER_ZODIAC_NPC_A","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L26_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"망할 꼰대들. 지들 일 아니라고 아무렇게 말하는 거 봐.","JPN":"くそジジイども。自分たちのことじゃないからって適当に。","ENG":"Damn geezers. Easy for them to talk when it's not their lives on the line.","TWN":"該死的老頑固。看他們隨便說話，因為這不是他們的事。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_HATE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L27_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"레드시프트가 뉘 집 개 이름이야? 잡아 오라면 잡아오게?","JPN":"レッドシフトがそう簡単に倒せるならこっちだって苦労してないわよ。","ENG":"Do they really think I can just catch Red Shift like that?","TWN":"紅移是誰家的狗嗎？說抓就抓？"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L28_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"하아…….","JPN":"はあ……","ENG":"*Sigh...*","TWN":"哀……"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L30_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"줄리아가 부상을 당한 상황이니, 내가 가세한들 카란티시르를 제압하는 건 어려워.","JPN":"ジュリアは怪我をしてるし、私が加勢してもカランティシルを制圧するのは難しいわ。","ENG":"With Julia wounded, even if I join the fight, taking down Carantisir won't be easy.","TWN":"茱莉亞受了傷，即使我加入也很難制服卡蘭堤西爾。"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"CARANTISIR_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L32_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"아셀라라는 녀석은 다른 아이들이 막아낼 수 있겠지만, 문제는 그 아이가 다루는 <color=#ffd34c>부활의 지팡이.</color>","JPN":"アセッラってやつは他の子たちでも止められるはずだけど、問題はあの子が扱ってる<color=#ffd34c>復活の杖</color>。","ENG":"Ascella might be manageable for the others, but the real issue is that <color=#ffd34c>Staff of Resurrection</color> she's wielding.","TWN":"亞瑟拉這個傢伙其他人可以擋住，但問題是她使用的<color=#ffd34c>復活之杖。</color>"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ASCELLA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L33_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"그리고… 다른 레드시프트 단원들이 언제든 움직일 수 있다는 점인가.","JPN":"あとは……他のレッドシフト団員たちがいつでも動けるという点かしら。","ENG":"And... the fact that the other Red Shift members could jump in at any time.","TWN":"還有……其他紅移小隊成員隨時可以行動嗎？"},"stage":{"bg":"BLACK","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"ASCELLA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_IDLE"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L34_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"뭐, 저쪽은 완전 개인주의니 단장이 위기여도 신경 쓰지는 않을 것 같지만…….","JPN":"まあ、あっちは完全に個人主義だし、団長がピンチでも気にしなさそうけど……","ENG":"Not that they'd care if their captain's in danger. Bunch of hardcore individualists over there...","TWN":"嗯，那邊完全是個人主義，就算團長有危機也不會在意吧……"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_DESPAIR"},"R":null}}},{"id":"L35_1","type":"dialog","speaker":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","text":{"KOREA":"어느 쪽이든 귀찮은 건 변함없네, 제길.","JPN":"どっちも面倒なのは一緒ね、くそ。","ENG":"Either way, it's going to be a hassle, shucks.","TWN":"不管是哪一邊，麻煩都是一樣的，真是的。"},"stage":{"bg":"CHURCH_KNIGHT","slots":{"L":null,"C":{"char_id":"MEDEA_ZODIAC_NULL_NULL","face":"UNIT_HATE"},"R":null}}}]`);export{e as default};